PackIt - Help create RiscPkg packages
#Parent StrongHelp:!Menu
#fH2:PackIt

A Utility program to help with the creation of packages
for the <RISC OS Packaging project=>#URL https://sites.google.com/site/alansriscosstuff/risc-os-packaging/risc-os-packaging-project>.

